      <scopecontent id="aspace_01b442bcb4f9b5bee1ed11a580fc618e">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>Photographic prints and clippings relating to English and American Drama as collected by Jack Randall Crawford, the staff of the Drama Library, and others.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
      <arrangement id="aspace_b2418f3bc5952cc71119eaefae6cbcc1">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>Arranged in ten series: I. Scenes from Early Plays to 1850. II. Scenes from American Plays, 1850-1979. III. Scenes from English Plays, (-1876)-1986. IV. Scenes from American Musical Comedies, (-1870)-1980. V. Scenes from English Musical Comedies, 1850-1971. VI. Designers (Scene, Costume, and Theatre Architects). VII. Costumes, (Greek-1953). VIII. Shakespeare's Plays, A-Z. IX. Film Scenes, Early Films-1979. X. Index.</p>  
      </arrangement>
